$ System.Char (struct)

`System.Char` is a UTF-16 (always?) encoded character.

sa:

  The default character size on a system can be determined with → Microsoft/dot-net/namespaces-classes/System/Runtime/InteropServices/Marshal/_CharSize[`System.Runtime.InteropServices.Marshal.SystemDefaultCharSize`].

  → Microsoft/dot-net/namespaces-classes/System/String[`System.String`] and its method → Microsoft/dot-net/namespaces-classes/System/String/ToCharArray[`ToCharArray`]
